data.description:
Multiple offers received.  Highest and Best offers due by 8pm 2/16/24. OVER 1/2 ACRE LOT in desirable Clemens-Munsinger garden neighborhood!  A short walk to both Munsinger gardens and Riverside park! One level living, with everything you need on main level! 3 bedrooms on one level! Front porch, Hardwood floors, window treatments, built-in bookshelves, main floor laundry. The lower level is finished and ready to be customized to your needs, with a full bath, a legal bedroom, a non-egress room, a large family room and tons of storage space! Bonus room downstairs could be a  game room or exercise room.  Oversized attached 2-stall garage with built-in workshop/shelving. Oversized concrete driveway with extra parking area. Well-maintained storage shed and concrete patio in the back yard. Breezeway from garage to house!
New furnace and Central AC installed in 2018! Move right in and enjoy!
